  <div class="container">
    <h3>
      ASK DEFINITION
    </h3>
    <br>
      <p>ACTIONABLE, SPECIFIC, KIND
      Do you have an action you can share with your pair that will help them to grow in their dev journey?<br>
      How will this action help them?
      It's important to be clear, concise and use concrete examples to show what action you are reffering to.
      Most importantly, how would you feel if you recieved this feedback?<br>
      Is your feedback kind to your pair's feelings and integrity?
      Is your feedback kind to your pair's learning and progress?
      </b></p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <form class="form" action="/ask/{{id}}" method="post">
    <label>
      Enter your feedback here:
      <input type="text" name="feedback">
    </label>
    
    <label for="checks">
      Is it actionable?
      <input id="actionable" type="checkbox" name="actioble" value="1">
      Is it specific?
      <input id="specific" type="checkbox" name="specific" value="1">
      Is it kind?
      <input id="kind" type="checkbox" name="kind" value="1">
    </label>
    
    <label>
      Which student would you like to send feedback to?
      <select name="id">
        {{#each students}}
        <option value={{id}}>{{name}}</option>
        {{/each}}
      </select>
    </label>
    
    <input type="submit" name="" value="Submit">
    </form>
  </div>
